CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,FA man from Berkshire on holiday in
OL,8,FDubai says the situation is 'surreal'
OL,9,Ffollowing attacks from Iran.
OL,11,FSimon Rourke, from Swallowfield near
OL,12,FReading, is currently in the country
OL,13,Fwith friends.
OL,15,FHis hotel was struck by an Iranian
OL,16,Fdrone at the weekend.
OL,18,FLuckily, they were in the desert at
OL,19,Fthe time, but when they returned to
OL,20,Fthe hotel they found one of the rooms
OL,21,Fthey were staying in obliterated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,FThey, along with others, were then
OL,8,Frushed to a different hotel and then
OL,9,Fdown to the basement to wait out the
OL,10,Fstrikes, and ended up spending a whole
OL,11,Fnight sheltering from the Iranian
OL,12,Fattack.
OL,14,FEveryone was okay, and Simon told ITV
OL,15,FMeridian the entire situation was
OL,16,F'surreal'. He said: "It was very
OL,17,Ffrightening, one of our rooms was
OL,18,Fobliterated, but luckily the rest were
OL,19,Fokay.
OL,26,@xD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,F"We weren't allowed into the hotel for
OL,8,Fa few hours, so we had to go and wait
OL,9,Fin the lobby of another hotel. Then we
OL,10,Fgot sent to the basement of the hotel
OL,11,Fbefore we eventually got back into
OL,12,Fhere.
OL,14,F"It was all surreal, we didn't really
OL,15,Fthink of the seriousness of it. We
OL,16,Fwere sat on the balcony having a drink
OL,17,Fand enjoying ourselves, and you could
OL,18,Fsee the drones being intercepted
OL,19,Ffurther out and going off. It was like
OL,20,Flittle fireworks.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,F"And then a missile came straight past
OL,8,Fthe front of the hotel and exploded
OL,9,Ffurther down the road, so at that
OL,10,Fpoint it was very obvious what was
OL,11,Fhappening.
OL,13,F"So, we went to the basement and spent
OL,14,Fthe night in the basement along with
OL,15,Fthe rest of the hotel."
OL,17,FSimon and his friends were due to fly
OL,18,Fback to the UK today (Monday 2 March),
OL,19,Fbut with all flights between the UK
OL,20,Fand the UAE cancelled, they're
OL,21,Fcurrently stuck in the country.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,FThey have been told it could be
OL,8,Fanother week until they can fly home.
OL,9,FBut, despite the delay, they're
OL,10,Fstaying positive.
OL,12,FSimon added: "We're all self-employed,
OL,13,Fwe all own our own companies, we're
OL,14,Fall sort of older men, so we're okay.
OL,16,F"It's just everyone's loved ones are
OL,17,Fsort of phoning through and worrying
OL,18,Fand trying to find ways of getting us
OL,19,Fhome. There's been talk of renting
OL,20,Ffour-wheel drives and driving through
OL,21,Fthe desert."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,FDaniel Moon, from Brighton, travelled
OL,8,Fto Dubai last Wednesday. He was due to
OL,9,Ffly back to Heathrow this morning with
OL,10,FBritish Airways, but the flight was
OL,11,Fcancelled.
OL,13,FHe's in good spirits despite the
OL,14,Fongoing disruption, caused by the
OL,15,FIranian attacks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,FHowever, Daniel is diabetic, and
OL,8,Frelies on insulin to manage his
OL,9,Fcondition. He can get more in Dubai,
OL,10,Fbut it isn't an easy process, leaving
OL,11,Fhim a little concerned about how long
OL,12,Fthey may be stuck in the country.
OL,14,FHe's waiting on British Airways to
OL,15,Fbook him onto a flight, which could be
OL,16,Fin a few days, or a few weeks.
OL,18,FHe said: "I'm diabetic. So I've got
OL,19,Finsulin and everything here, but I'm
OL,20,Fon my last five days.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,F"So I don't really want to be here
OL,8,Fmore than five days. I'm going to have
OL,9,Fto spend a lot and find a doctor for
OL,10,Fmedical stuff.
OL,12,F"But it is the stress of not knowing
OL,13,Fhow and when we're going to get home.
OL,14,FAnd the wait for that, you know, a
OL,15,Fplane from Heathrow and crews have got
OL,16,Fto get here, you know, they've got to
OL,17,Fplan at least a day in advance.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,F"So it's the stress of just being
OL,8,Fstuck here and the worry going to run
OL,9,Fout of medicine if we're going to be
OL,10,Fmore than the next four or five days."
OL,12,FFlights from London Heathrow and
OL,13,FLondon Gatwick to many Arab countries
OL,14,Fremain suspended, following the
OL,15,Fattacks, which began at the weekend.
OL,17,FAirspace above multiple countries in
OL,18,Fthe Middle East is closed, disrupting
OL,19,Fhundreds of thousands of airline
OL,20,Fpassengers globally.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
