OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772464379
OL,3,CNear miss for Berkshire man after
OL,4,Chotel room 'obliterated' by Iranian
OL,5,Cdrone
OL,7,FBritish Airways, which flies from
OL,8,FHeathrow, said it is 'closely
OL,9,Fmonitoring the situation' and has
OL,10,Fcancelled 'a number of our flights to
OL,11,Fthe Middle East'.
OL,13,FVirgin Atlantic also axed two flights
OL,14,Fto Heathrow on Monday, one from each
OL,15,Fof Dubai, UAE and Riyadh, Saudi
OL,16,FArabia, while others were rerouted.
OL,18,FQatar Airways said on Monday morning
OL,19,Fthat all its flights remain suspended.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
